                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee> the within letter you will\n                                                  <sic>persive</sic> how <persName>Mr\n                                                  Kohen</persName> acted<lb/> contrary to the\n                                        station he was in also the wrong the writer of the\n                                        letter<lb/> has done <del>to give</del> on giving\n                                                  <persName>Mr Cohen</persName>\n                                        <add>Hebrew</add> if you think it proper<lb/> to and for the\n                                        Good of <placeName>Israel</placeName>. I think it would do\n                                        good<lb/> to Expose both of the <sic>offenters</sic>\n                                        <sic>trough</sic> your Occident<lb/> I only make the remark\n                                        and leave it at your<lb/>\n                                        <sic>disgresion</sic> yours very Respectfully</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">N Gallinger</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p\n                                        rend=\"The following address is written sideways near the right side of the page\">\n                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p\n                                        rend=\"The following address is written sideways near the right side of the page\"\n                                        >favor of <persName role=\"author\">Mr. N. Galinger</persName>\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia. Pa.</placeName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3348h76k/canvas/p2"
